      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Detachable lengths of tubing inserted into aerophones, either permanently or for a specific playing occasion, for the purpose of either changing the sounding tube length, or to carry the mouthpiece where it is within easier reach of the player.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
